			SAMPy Client package providing a very small VO
			interactivity using the SAMP protocol. This allows
			anyone to easily send and receive data to VO
			applications such as Aladin, Topcat or DS9.
			</p>
			<b><a href='https://github.com/mfouesneau/ezmap'>EZMAP</a></b>
			<p class='description'>
			make python parallel mapping even simpler
			Everything goes through the same command: <i>map</i>!
			which also includes a progress indicator.
			</p>

			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">

